# Variables

* Variables are used to **store values**. They can be **any data type**.  
* Variable names cannot start with a letter or an underscore. They can only contain alphanumeric (1, 2, a, b, A, B, etc.) characters and underscore.  
  **CAUTION\!\!** They are **case sensitive**\!\!.   
* Examples:

* **CAUTION\!\!** When concatenating (adding together) variables, make sure **theyâ€™re of the same data type**.
